{
  "stem": "14156.4",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 34,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And he went right away and took this, brought me back another pair of shoes, and then he went to the-- to the kitchen, wherever, and showed.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So they gave him bread.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They have him a-- a salami that long, bacon, and all kinds of stuff.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Now, how are we going to save this stuff?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Where-- where are we going to put it?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But we-- All we did, we could do, we put it under our pillows in the back.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Sleep on it so nobody will steal it again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Well, it was good for a few days.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We ate, we give away a little here and there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And-- and here we went.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Then I ended up-- from there, I ended up in Wien Meidling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Another long-- we want to go on?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "How did you get there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By train.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They took us from there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They put us to Wien Meidling.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There, we worked.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "As I found out a few days ago, it was the first German jet was built by Messerschmidt.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] We didn't know what it was.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know either.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "There was no-- there was an engine in the back, a hole in the back.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no propeller.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the-- the-- the were put on outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was down in the ground.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was a-- it was a cave.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Used to be a cave.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And what--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Where I worked, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I also got my first lesson in being-- being whipped.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, the-- we had to have a-- a-- a-- a little piece of cloth what was showing what is a-- it's one triangle.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "It's red.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the opposite triangle is yellow, what shows you that you are Jewish.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't have no sew.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean-- didn't have needle and anything.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
